'''城市足球集團'''（City Football Group）簡稱CFG，是一家管理足球俱樂部的控股公司。集團由三個財團共同擁有，包括主投資者{{le|阿布扎比聯合財團|Abu Dhabi United Group}}(ADUG)擁有78%股份，[[華人文化產業投資基金|華人文化產業投資基金]]及[[中國中信集團|中國中信集團]]共同擁有12%，最後10%由{{le|銀湖投資集團|Silver Lake (investment firm)}}持有。<ref name="AmericaInvestment">{{cite web|url=https://www.cityfootballgroup.com/information-resource/news-and-press-packs/cfg-announces-us-500-million-strategic-investment-by-silver-lake/|title=CFG Announces US$500 Million Strategic Investment by Silver Lake|last=|first=|date=27 November 2019|work=|access-date=|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112014617/https://www.cityfootballgroup.com/information-resource/news-and-press-packs/cfg-announces-us-500-million-strategic-investment-by-silver-lake/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ChinaInvestment">{{cite web |url=http://www.mcfc.co.uk/News/Club-news/2015/December/CFG-statement-1-December-2015/1448953247 |title=CFG Statement: 1 December 2015 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160208130921/http://www.mcfc.co.uk/news/club-news/2015/december/cfg-statement-1-december-2015/1448953247 |archivedate=2016-02-08 |work=mcfc.co.uk |date=1 December 2015 |accessdate=1 December 2015 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在全球各地經營多間足球俱樂部，集團的主要俱樂部是在[[英格兰足球超级联赛|英格兰足球超级联赛]]作賽的[[曼徹斯特城足球會|曼徹斯特城足球會]]，另外集團還擁有美國，澳洲，印度，日本，西班牙，烏拉圭，中國和比利時的俱樂部的股份。集團最初的目標是在每一個大洲都擁有一個俱樂部，每個俱樂部的名稱中都帶有標識“ City”。<ref name="china">{{cite web|last1=Delaney|first1=Miguel|title=Manchester City ownership group plans Chinese Super League expansion|url=http://www.espnfc.us/manchester-city/story/2832405/manchester-city-ownership-group-planning-china-expansion|website=ESPNFC|publisher=ESPN|accessdate=23 March 2017|archive-date=2016-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320170419/http://www.espnfc.us/manchester-city/story/2832405/manchester-city-ownership-group-planning-china-expansion|dead-url=no}}</ref>

