e-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006121339/http://www.mlssoccer.com/news/article/2013/03/17/mls-commissioner-don-garber-talks-nyc2-progress-florida-expansion-champions-|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://appext20.dos.ny.gov/corp_public/CORPSEARCH.ENTITY_INFORMATION?p_nameid=4396707&p_corpid=4399753&p_entity_name=new%20york%20city%20football%20club&p_name_type=A&p_search_type=BEGINS&p_srch_results_page=0 |title=Entity Information |accessdate=25 May 2013 |work=NYS Division of Corporations, State Records and UCC |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306131354/https://appext20.dos.ny.gov/corp_public/CORPSEARCH.ENTITY_INFORMATION?p_nameid=4396707&p_corpid=4399753&p_entity_name=new%20york%20city%20football%20club&p_name_type=A&p_search_type=BEGINS&p_srch_results_page=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>其後於5月21日正式宣布[[紐約城足球俱樂部|紐約城足球俱樂部]]成為第20個加入美國職業足球大聯盟的俱樂部。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mlssoccer.com/news/article/2013/05/21/major-league-soccer-announces-new-york-expansion-team-new-york-city-football|title=Major League Soccer announces New York City FC expansion team: New York City FC|date=21 May 2013|work=mlssoccer.com|accessdate=21 May 2013|archive-date=2013-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607111330/http://www.mlssoccer.com/news/article/2013/05/21/major-league-soccer-announces-new-york-expansion-team-new-york-city-football|dead-url=no}}</ref> 為了將俱樂部與其曼彻斯特城聯繫起來，新的美國職業足球大聯盟球隊被聘為前曼彻斯特城，前美國職業足球大聯盟和前美國國家隊球員[[克劳迪奥·雷纳|克劳迪奥·雷纳]]成為首位僱員，擔任足球總監。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mlssoccer.com/news/article/2013/05/22/new-york-city-fc-name-claudio-reyna-director-football-operations |title=New York City FC name Marcin Baszczynski director of football operations |date=May 22, 2013 |work=mlssoccer.com |accessdate=May 22, 2013 |archive-date=2013-05-27 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6GwGJT29q?url=http://www.mlssoccer.com/news/article/2013/05/22/new-york-city-fc-name-claudio-reyna-director-football-operations |dead-url=no }}</ref>與此同時，簽下{{le|傑森·克雷斯|Jason Kreis}}擔任球隊的第一任主教練。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nycfc.com/News/Latest-News/2013/December/Head-Coach? |title=Jason Kreis named as Head Coach |date=December 11, 2013 |accessdate=December 11, 2013 |work=nycfc.com |archive-date=2014-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140729102546/http://nycfc.com/News/Latest-News/2013/December/Head-Coach |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2016年，曼彻斯特城的青訓經理[[帕特里克·维埃拉|帕特里克·维埃拉]]將轉到[[紐約城足球俱樂部|紐約城足球俱樂部]]擔任主教練。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nycfc.com/post/2015/11/09/patrick-vieira-appointed-new-york-city-fc-head-coach|title=Patrick Vieira appointed as New York City FC Head Coach|website=nycfc.com|date=November 9, 2015|accessdate=March 23, 2017|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108150225/https://www.nycfc.com/post/2015/11/09/patrick-vieira-appointed-new-york-city-fc-head-coach|dead-url=no}}</ref>2021年12月12日總決賽，擁主場之利的波特蘭伐木者迎戰紐約城先失守下，於補時階段追和，兩軍激戰120分鐘仍未分勝負，最終成立僅7年的紐約城互射12碼以4：2凱旋，首奪美職總冠軍。<ref>{{Cite web|title=美職｜紐約城成軍7年首奪總冠軍 曼城致賀 城市足球集團5軍年內稱霸 (19:49) - 20211212 - 體育|url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e9%ab%94%e8%82%b2/article/20211212/s00006/1639295272035/%e7%be%8e%e8%81%b7-%e7%b4%90%e7%b4%84%e5%9f%8e%e6%88%90%e8%bb%8d7%e5%b9%b4%e9%a6%96%e5%a5%aa%e7%b8%bd%e5%86%a0%e8%bb%8d-%e6%9b%bc%e5%9f%8e%e8%87%b4%e8%b3%80-%e5%9f%8e%e5%b8%82%e8%b6%b3%e7%90%83%e9%9b%86%e5%9c%985%e8%bb%8d%e5%b9%b4%e5%85%a7%e7%a8%b1%e9%9c%b8|access-date=2021-12-14|work=明報新聞網 - 即時新聞 instant news|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2021-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211214013150/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e9%ab%94%e8%82%b2/article/20211212/s00006/1639295272035/%e7%be%8e%e8%81%b7-%e7%b4%90%e7%b4%84%e5%9f%8e%e6%88%90%e8%bb%8d7%e5%b9%b4%e9%a6%96%e5%a5%aa%e7%b8%bd%e5%86%a0%e8%bb%8d-%e6%9b%bc%e5%9f%8e%e8%87%b4%e8%b3%80-%e5%9f%8e%e5%b8%82%e8%b6%b3%e7%90%83%e9%9b%86%e5%9c%985%e8%bb%8d%e5%b9%b4%e5%85%a7%e7%a8%b1%e9%9c%b8}}</ref>

